author: Home Repair Tutor
description: ZipWall dust barrier zipper kit…I measure and mark where I want the door. Then I bond the heavy duty zippers to 4 mil plastic. I love these doors because they can be up when not in use and contain all the dust to one area. You can find them at Lowe’s in the paint section 🔥 Many thanks to ZipWall for for sponsoring this video and keeping work areas safe ❤️#dustbarrier #dustcontrol #zipwall #homerenovation #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
